graph TD
    A[Input Shelf Image] --> B[Image Resizing & Preprocessing]
    B --> C[DETR SKU-110K Object Detector]
    C --> D[Non-Max Suppression NMS]
    D --> E[Product Bounding Boxes]
    E --> F[Product Cropping]
    E --> J[Shelf Row DBSCAN Clustering]
    F --> G[CLIP Brand Classifier]
    G --> H[Zero-Shot Class Probabilities]
    H --> I{Score >= 0.4?}
    I -- Yes --> K[Assign Class: Lays, Doritos, Coke, Pepsi]
    I -- No --> L[Assign Class: Other]
    K --> M[Brand Labels]
    L --> M
    A --> N[EasyOCR Engine]
    N --> O[Raw OCR Detections]
    O --> P[Regex Price Tag Cleaning]
    P --> Q[Clean Price Labels]
    J --> R[Row Midpoints & Layout]
    M --> S[Share of Shelf SOS Math]
    R --> S
    S --> T[Business Metrics Compilation]
    Q --> T
    T --> U[JSON Metrics Output]
    M --> V[OpenCV Visual Overlay Rendering]
    R --> V
    Q --> V
    V --> W[Annotated Overlay Image]

    style A fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style U fill:#85C1E9,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style W fill:#82E0AA,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
